            <subjectClass>인사(人事)</subjectClass>
            <subjectClass>외교-야(野)</subjectClass>
          </biblioData>
        </front>
        <text>
          <content>
            <paragraph align="center">○以<index num="1923474_0" ref="M_0002615" sort="K" type="이름">朴宗薰</index>爲告訃兼奏請使, <index num="1923475_0" ref="M_0005539" sort="K" type="이름">李羲準</index>爲副使, <index num="1923476_0" ref="M_0002893" sort="K" type="이름">成遂默</index>, 爲書狀官。</paragraph>
          </content>
        </text>
      </level5>
      <level5 id="wxa_10011018_004">
        <front>
          <biblioData type="T">
            <title>
              <mainTitle>감군 순장에게 명하여 공제 전에는 그대로 번을 들게 하다</mainTitle>
            </title>
            <docNo level="n" name="titleno">004</docNo>
